OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA dry
OL,6,Fand bright start on Wednesday, but
OL,7,Frain later. Rain or showers on
OL,8,FThursday and Friday, which may be
OL,9,Fheavy. Winds strengthening on Friday,
OL,10,Fgales possible.
